H3.text: The Fitzwilliam Museum is in which British town or city. Cambridge

A4.text: The Fitzwilliam Museum is the art and antiquities museum of the University of Cambridge.

A5.text: It is located on Trumpington Street opposite Fitzwilliam Street in central Cambridge.
